e. Congenital bronchiectasis
f. Atelectasis
2. Post infection conditions
a. Necrotising pneumonia caused by bacteria (Myocobacteriumtuberculosis, Staphylococcus aureus, Haemophilus influenza and Pseudomonas), viral (HIV, adenoviruses and influenzae), fungal (Aspergillus)
